twitchData.description: I'm an RPG fan with a passion for characters, stories & fictional worlds. I make an episodic 2D fantasy RPG series called Raindrop Chronicles with my Twitch community. Come hang out with us and help us shape the story, characters, quests, dialogue, scenes, maps, worldbuilding, features... and more!
